description:
Couple swapping, wife swapping or even girlfriend swapping is on the rise in india. Its still not openly discussed but the number of people involved has increased. There are wife swapping parties, couple swapping parties happening every weekend in one place or the other. The trend has picked up so much that even girlfriend and boyfriends now swap. Many believe its not cheating and better than having an extramarital affair. 
We asked people what there views on swapping were and the results were not unexpected.right from college girls, working women, men all had their point of view. Is india really going ahead?
fulltitle: Would You Do Couple Swapping/ Wife Swapping? Shocking Reactions on Street Interview
